data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this stunning five-bed, three-bath home located in the heart of Avon, Minnesota. This home features a new center island, a beautiful open floor plan concept, brand new mechanicals and oversized bedrooms. These provide comfort and flexibility, accommodating various lifestyles. Escape to the expansive fenced backyard, offering privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary of its own, featuring generous proportions and an en-suite bathroom for added convenience. With three bathrooms, mornings are a breeze for a busy household. You will enjoy having an oversized garage for extra storage as well. Located in Avon, enjoy the charm of small-town living while having easy access to local amenities and services. This residence seamlessly blends modern comforts with practical design presenting an ideal backdrop for a vibrant and contemporary lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
